Initialization

Around January 2019, I started playing a Custom Game mode in Dota 2 that was taking a large section of the gaming community by storm, Dota Autochess by Studio Drodo. The game mode was a polished version built ontop of Pokemon TD from Warcraft3 and Casino TD from Starcraft 2. When playing the game, I was inspired to do a single-player spin on the game and I got to work to paper prototype and create my vision game within Unity.
